homeschooltracker.content.Task

  • Packages that use Task 
    Package Description
    homeschooltracker.content
    This package holds the abstract and concrete content for the Subjects, Lessons, and Materials.
    homeschooltracker.content.subjects.grade1
    This package contains concrete Subjects for Grade 1.
    homeschooltracker.content.subjects.grade2
    This package contains concrete Subjects for Grade 2.
    homeschooltracker.content.taskState
    This package holds all possible states for a Task.
    homeschooltracker.gui
    This package handles the graphical user interface for the Homeschool Tracker program.
    homeschooltracker.users
    This package holds the users, Parent and Student, that interact with the application.
